title: Comedian's spoof of Johnson's lockdown message goes viral
description: British comedian Matt Lucas took aim at the British Prime Minister's speech to the nation in a video that went viral on social media.

title: Why this movie has been playing for 24 years
description: "Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge" is an iconic part of Indian cinema, and has changed rom-coms forever. It's so beloved that it has screened every day, for more than 24 years, at the Maratha Mandir theater in Mumbai.

title: This man only wears two colors. Here's why
description: Seven, yes, that's his real name, is known throughout Bangalore, India, as the man who only wears red and white.

title: Why one man owns 2,371 cell phones
description: Jayesh Kale is a collector in India who has spent at least five years gathering cell phones, calling the devices in the collection his "babies."
